mintInvoice.t.sol
├── when the caller IS NOT the authorized Relayer
│   └── it should revert with the {Unathorized} error
└── when the caller IS the authorized Relayer
    ├── it should emit the {InvoiceMinted} event
    ├── it should set the `paymentRequestId` for the `tokenId`
    ├── it should mint the invoice NFT to the payment recipient
    └── it should set the `tokenURI` for the `tokenId`